data.description: If you are looking for wooded Colorado acreage with views, this is it!  Take a leisurely soak in the hot tub on the 30' newly replaced deck, watch the wildlife and take in the views of the West Elks, Black Canyon, Grand Mesa, San Juans and the valley below. One wall in the Great Room is covered with reclaimed barn wood all which has been gathered from local properties. The three bedrooms include two master suites and an extra shower in the laundry room which is connected to bedroom #3.  The open living, kitchen & dining areas with spacious windows create great natural light and mountain views from the inside. There are two detached garages with 5 bays, a workshop area and RV hook up. Bring your toys, animals and hobbies to this unique, comfortable, mountain side home. Some furniture is negotiable. Easy access to Cedaredge, Delta and Grand Mesa.
